      </table>
     </div>
      </td>
     </tr>
     <tr>
      <td>Server Hardware</td>
      <td>
       <span class='hardware-48 icon-48'/>
      </td>
      <td>
       <ul>
        <li>
          Intel Pentium 4, 2.0 Ghz or higher (Dual 2.0 GHz recommended)
        </li>
        <li>
          2GB of RAM (4.0 Gb recommended)
        </li>
        <li>300 MB of available hard-disk space for system storage</li>
        <li>2 Gb of available hard-disk space for data storage (5 Gb or more recommended)</li>
       </ul>
       Actual requirements for a specific project may differ.
      </td>
     </tr>

     <tr>
      <td>Java</td>
     <td>
      <a href='http://java.com/'><img src='../../images/java_logo.png' alt='Java logo'/></a>
     </td>
     <td>
          <a href='http://java.com/en/download/help/'>Sun's Java Virtual Machine</a>, JVM 6 (or 5). 
          The JVM is also called the Java Runtime Environment (JRE) or just Java.
          The Java Development Kit (JDK) contains the JVM.
   
     <div class='nav'>
      <table>
       <tr>
        <td>
         <a href='http://java.com/en/download/index.jsp'><img src='../../images/sun_logo_tiny.png' alt='Sun logo'/></a>
