     </div>
    </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td>Servlet container</td>
   <td>
     <a href='http://java.com/'><img src='../../images/java_logo.png' alt='Java logo'/></a>
   </td>
   <td>Hippo CMS works in any Java Servlet container or Java application server conforming to version
       <span class='confirm'>2.4</span> of the 
       <a href='http://java.sun.com/products/servlet/reference/api/index.html'>Sun Servlet container 
       specification</a>, E.g.:

       <div class='nav'>
        <table>
         <tr>
          <td>
           <a href='http://jetty.mortbay.com/jetty/'><img src='../../images/jetty_logo_tiny.png' alt='Jetty logo'/></a>
          </td>
          <td>
           <a href='http://jetty.mortbay.com/jetty/'>Jetty</a> <a href='http://docs.codehaus.org/display/JETTY/Downloading+Jetty'>6.1</a>,
             also included in <a href='../quickstart.html'>Hippo CMS quickstart-bin package</a>.
          </td>
         </tr>
         <tr>
          <td>
           <a href='http://tomcat.apache.org/'><img src='../../images/tomcat_logo_tiny.png' alt='Tomcat logo'/></a>
          </td>
          <td>
           <a href='http://tomcat.apache.org/'>Tomcat</a> <a href="http://tomcat.apache.org/download-60.cgi">6.0</a> and 5.5                
          </td>
         </tr>
         <tr>
          <td>
           <a href='https://glassfish.dev.java.net/public/users.html'><img src='../../images/glassfish_logo_tiny.png' alt='Glassfish logo'/></a>
          </td>
          <td>
           <a href='https://glassfish.dev.java.net/public/users.html'>Sun GlassFish</a> V2 (<a href='http://packages.ubuntu.com/hardy/glassfishv2'>Linux Ubuntu package of Glassfish V2</a>). 
          </td>
         </tr>
        </table>
       </div>
    </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td>Database</td>
    <td>
     <span class='archive-48 icon-48'/>
    </td>
    <td>
        Hippo CMS uses a relational database for it's datastorage, E.g.:
       <div class='nav'>
        <table>
         <tr>
          <td>
           <a href='http://db.apache.org/derby/'><img src='../../images/derby_logo_tiny.png' alt='Derby logo'/></a>
          </td>
          <td>
          <a href='http://db.apache.org/derby/'>Apache Derby</a> &gt; 10.0
            is embedded and configured as default and runs "out of the box".
          </td>
         </tr>
         <tr>
          <td>
          </td>
          <td>
           <a href="http://www.mysql.com">MySQL 5.0</a> and <a href="http://www.mysql.com">5.1</a>
          </td>
         </tr>
         <tr>
          <td>
          </td>
          <td>
            PosgreSQL 8.0 or newer
          </td>
         </tr>
         <tr>
          <td>
           <a href='http://www.oracle.com/index.html'><img src='../../images/oracle_logo_tiny.png' alt='Oracle logo'/></a>
          </td>
          <td>Oracle 9.2, 10 and 11</td>
         </tr>
         <tr>
          <td>
          </td>
          <td>MS SQLServer 2000 or newer</td>
         </tr>
        </table>
       </div>
   </td>
   </tr>
  </table>
  </div>
